entry.title: U.K. Provides Ukraine With Long-Range Attack Drones
entry.content: President Volodymyr Zelensky visited Britain as part of a tour of Ukraine’s European allies aimed at replenishing the country’s war chest ahead of a planned counteroffensive.

entry.title: 'Bakhmut Trap': Ukrainian Advances Vindicate Defense of Besieged City
entry.content: Ukrainian commanders say recent advances are proof that their strategy—to hold on to the city for as long as possible—is paying off.

entry.title: How to Get Your Health Insurance to Cover Ozempic and Other Drugs Used for Weight Loss
entry.content: Insurers and employers often put up hurdles when patients seek access to Ozempic, Wegovy or another costly prescription drug to help with weight loss. But there are ways to get your health plan to pay, if you qualify.
